"{\"uid\": \"jamaicaobserver.com-2024-07-30-olympic-mens-triathlon-postponed-seine-fails-water-tests\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"PARIS, France (AFP) - The Paris Olympics men's triathlon was postponed just hours before it was due to get under way on Tuesday after water quality tests on the River Seine revealed it was still too dirty for swimming, organisers said.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 235, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7, \"end\": 13, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999998111179772, \"rank\": 1.8790747155269893e-07, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 161, \"end\": 172, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"River Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"PARIS\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 5}, {\"ngram\": \"AFP\", \"from\": 15, \"to\": 18}, {\"ngram\": \"The Paris Olympics men's triathlon\", \"from\": 22, \"to\": 56}, {\"ngram\": \"way\", \"from\": 113, \"to\": 116}, {\"ngram\": \"Tuesday\", \"from\": 120, \"to\": 127}, {\"ngram\": \"water quality tests\", \"from\": 134, \"to\": 153}, {\"ngram\": \"swimming\", \"from\": 209, \"to\": 217}, {\"ngram\": \"organisers\", \"from\": 219, \"to\": 229}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a move that left some athletes angry and Olympic officials scrambling, organisers announced shortly before 5:00 am (0300 GMT) that the men's event would be delayed by 24 hours.\", \"from\": 237, \"to\": 416, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 361, \"end\": 364, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greenwich_Mean_Time\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.0977594286298e-17, \"text\": \"GMT\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greenwich_Mean_Time\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greenwich_Mean_Time\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a move\", \"from\": 240, \"to\": 246}, {\"ngram\": \"some athletes\", \"from\": 257, \"to\": 270}, {\"ngram\": \"angry and Olympic officials\", \"from\": 271, \"to\": 298}, {\"ngram\": \"organisers\", \"from\": 311, \"to\": 321}, {\"ngram\": \"5:00 am\", \"from\": 347, \"to\": 354}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's event\", \"from\": 371, \"to\": 386}, {\"ngram\": \"24 hours\", \"from\": 407, \"to\": 415}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A joint statement from Paris 2024 and World Triathlon blamed heavy rain on Friday and Saturday, while forecasts of fresh storms later on Tuesday cast doubt on whether any outdoor swimming will be possible this week.\", \"from\": 418, \"to\": 633, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 456, \"end\": 471, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Triathlon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.1378007379507434e-15, \"text\": \"World Triathlon\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Triathlon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Triathlon\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A joint statement\", \"from\": 418, \"to\": 435}, {\"ngram\": \"Paris\", \"from\": 441, \"to\": 446}, {\"ngram\": \"heavy rain\", \"from\": 479, \"to\": 489}, {\"ngram\": \"Friday\", \"from\": 493, \"to\": 499}, {\"ngram\": \"Saturday\", \"from\": 504, \"to\": 512}, {\"ngram\": \"forecasts\", \"from\": 520, \"to\": 529}, {\"ngram\": \"fresh storms\", \"from\": 533, \"to\": 545}, {\"ngram\": \"Tuesday\", \"from\": 555, \"to\": 562}, {\"ngram\": \"doubt\", \"from\": 568, \"to\": 573}, {\"ngram\": \"any outdoor swimming\", \"from\": 585, \"to\": 605}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Paris 2024 and World Triathlon reiterate that their priority is the health of the athletes,\\\" the statement said after a meeting held at 3:30 am local time (0130 GMT) on Tuesday.\", \"from\": 635, \"to\": 813, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 651, \"end\": 666, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Triathlon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank